68
00:04:53,277 --> 00:04:55,477
Benarkah itu?

69
00:04:55,477 --> 00:04:56,877
Ya.

70
00:04:56,877 --> 00:04:59,677
Karena Tuan Agatsuma membuat keributan seperti itu,

71
00:04:59,677 --> 00:05:02,777
