139
00:08:26,077 --> 00:08:28,177
Nah, kartu tidak bisa dipikirkan.

140
00:08:28,177 --> 00:08:29,577
Oh?

141
00:08:29,577 --> 00:08:31,077
Karena jika demikian,

142
00:08:31,077 --> 00:08:33,777
