203
00:11:44,377 --> 00:11:46,777
yang memiliki dendam terhadap Tuan Agatsuma!

204
00:11:56,810 --> 00:11:59,710
Hei, ada apa denganmu?

205
00:11:59,710 --> 00:12:01,510
Tiba-tiba mengoceh dan mengoceh!

206
